<div id="content" class="content wikipage" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<p id="l1">
A light source located on a <a title="Drum Scanner" href="Drum_Scanner">drum scanner</a> used to view a <a title="Color Transparency" href="Color_Transparency">color transparency</a> mounted on the drum. The transparency viewing lamp is typically a <a title="5000 K" class="nonexistent" href="http://printwiki.org/5000_K">5000 K</a> fluorescent lamp and is larger than the light source used for the actual imaging. 
</p>
